OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet and rather windy day as
OL,6,Frain spreads steadily east. The rain
OL,7,Fturning heavy at times, but easing
OL,8,Flater from the west. Feeling muggy
OL,9,Funder widespread cloud cover, with
OL,10,Fpatchy coastal and hill fog, mainly in
OL,11,Fthe west.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain becoming
OL,14,Fincreasingly showery into the evening,
OL,15,Fhowever heavy bursts are still
OL,16,Fpossible. Drier later in the night
OL,17,Fwith some clear spells developing.
OL,18,FRemaining rather windy for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
