OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FRather cloudy in the south
OL,6,Fwith patchy rain in the west. Brighter
OL,7,Ffor northern areas with showers and
OL,8,Fsome sunny spells. Winds a little
OL,9,Flighter and feeling a touch warmer.
